}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;Pacenka, Steve (April 15, 1996).[http://www.lightlink.com/spacenka/fors/police/report-lazenby.html &quot;Report of Detective P. Lazenby&quot;] (archive). ([http://www.lightlink.com/spacenka/fors/ Case main])&lt;/ref&gt; Schwartz was originally convicted on three felony counts, with one reduced to a misdemeanor, but on February 1, 2007, his arrest and conviction records were sealed through an official [[expungement]], and he is legally no longer a felon.&lt;ref&gt;{{cite news
